title: Dog Breed - Pretrained keras models(LB 0.3)
description: Transfer learning with pretrained Keras modelsAlthough Kernel resources were increased recently we still can not train useful CNNs without GPU. The original ImageNet set has quite a few different dog classes so we can reuse CNNs with pretrained ImageNet weights. Fortunately prediction is much faster (<1s/image) making it possible to run meaningful experiments with Kaggle Kernels.
